program hello;

const
Message1='Hello,';
Message2='This is Bootnecklads first Script';
Message3='Goodbye';

procedure hello;
begin
  wait(1000)
   Writeln(Message1);
  wait(500)
   Writeln(Message2);
  wait(500)
   Writeln(Message3);
end;

begin
 repeat
  Hello;
 until(false)
end.[/code]

Basically it writes:
Hello,
This is Bootnecklads first Script
Goodbye

And repeats that until the script is stopped

